&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/details&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;multi-language-adaptation-of-categories&#34;&gt;Multi-language adaptation of categories&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I tried to use &lt;code&gt;_index.md&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;_index.en.md&lt;/code&gt; in the &lt;code&gt;test&lt;/code&gt; file in the &lt;code&gt;./content/categories&lt;/code&gt; directory, but the result was not what I expected. In the &lt;strong&gt;homepage category&lt;/strong&gt;, it can only be displayed as &lt;code&gt;test&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;test&lt;/code&gt;, and there is no multi-language adaptation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure 
	&gt;
	&lt;a href=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/14/wJNV8LWTyKCSsom.png&#34; &gt;
		&lt;img src=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/14/wJNV8LWTyKCSsom.png&#34;
			
			
			
